    {
      "id": "55fe93a4-ee52-4430-a7cc-c3b192a8cde2",
      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $A = \\begin{pmatrix} 0 &1      &       &(0)     \\cr\n                    1 &\\ddots &\\ddots          \\cr\n                      &\\ddots &\\ddots &1       \\cr\n                    (0)&      &1      &0       \\cr \\end{pmatrix} \\in \\mathcal{M}_n(\\R)$.",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(A = \\begin{pmatrix} 0 &amp;1      &amp;       &amp;(0)     \\cr\n                    1 &amp;\\ddots &amp;\\ddots          \\cr\n                      &amp;\\ddots &amp;\\ddots &amp;1       \\cr\n                    (0)&amp;      &amp;1      &amp;0       \\cr \\end{pmatrix} \\in \\mathcal{M}_n(\\R)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "90cb5a13-3b07-4dec-8404-e48245780774",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Calculer $D_n(\\theta) = \\det(A+(2\\cos\\theta) I)$ par récurrence.",
        "html": "<p>Calculer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(D_n(\\theta) = \\det(A+(2\\cos\\theta) I)\\)</span> par récurrence.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "6db99107-efac-4ea0-bfca-4fc4177d2cc8",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$D_n = 2\\cos\\theta D_{n-1} - D_{n-2}  \\Rightarrow \n              D_n = \\frac{\\sin(n+1)\\theta}{\\sin\\theta}$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(D_n = 2\\cos\\theta D_{n-1} - D_{n-2}  \\Rightarrow \n              D_n = \\frac{\\sin(n+1)\\theta}{\\sin\\theta}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "d7c88758-44ce-4842-8315-f4ffdb7c0257",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "En déduire les valeurs propres de $A$.",
        "html": "<p>En déduire les valeurs propres de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(A\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "d47c0394-abf1-4706-a82a-cb7b6f4c3693",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$-2\\cos\\left(\\frac{k\\pi}{n+1}\\right)$, $1 \\le k \\le n$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(-2\\cos\\left(\\frac{k\\pi}{n+1}\\right)\\)</span>, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(1 \\le k \\le n\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
  ]
